CCA.Eligibility:
Age >18 years;
Capable of informed consent;
Histologically-proven iCCA;
Complete surgical resection must be achievable;
No evidence of metastatic disease; 
ECOG 0 or 1

Closed.Eligibility:
Histologically-confirmed cholangio; 
locally or centrally confirmed IDH1 mutation
Treatment with up to one cycle of durvalumab plus gemcitabine/cisplatin treatment is permitted before study participation.
